uiet Sun\nphotosphere has far more unsigned magnetic flux and magnetic energy than the\nactive regions and the network all together.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2005 08:46:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
