arburst galaxies, thereby justifying the\nlabel of localized starbursts. Finally, we estimate the stability of the\ncomplexes, and find that they will probably loose a large fraction of their\nmass to the surrounding environment, although the central regions may merge\ninto a single large star cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2005 13:27:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
